rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Before it became like this, I wonder if this
place had trees and flowers, like Gula.

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0101
rows.name:
This is a water tower, right?
Why would something like this be here?

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0201
rows.name: Tora saw this in Gula, mo!

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0202
rows.name:
Maybe Eden was a place
like Gula, Mo-mo?

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0301
rows.name:
Did the people who lived in Eden
also store water in water towers?

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0302
rows.name: It seems we share some common culture.

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0401
rows.name: In Alst, we'd store water in this...

rows.label: tlk00000594_01_msg0402
rows.name:
But I wonder what the people here
put inside it...
